<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2074/98 of 29 September 1998 adjusting the standard amount provided for in Council Regulation (EEC) No 1010/86 and setting the production refund on white sugar used in the chemical industry </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 2074/98, millega kohandatakse n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 1010/86 etten&auml;htud standardsummat ja kehtestatakse keemiat&ouml;&ouml;stuses kasutatava valge suhkru tootmistoetus 29. september 1998 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 1010/86 of 25 March 1986 laying down general rules for the production refund on certain sugar products used in the chemical industry (1), as amended by Commission Regulation (EC) No 1148/98 (2), and in particular Article 4a(1a) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 25. m&auml;rtsi 1986. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1010/86, millega s&auml;testatakse teatavate keemiat&ouml;&ouml;stuses kasutatavate suhkrutoodete tootmistoetuse &uuml;ldeeskirjad, (1) muudetud komisjoni m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1148/98, (2) eriti selle artikli 4a l&otilde;iget 1a, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 1785/81 of 30 June 1981 on the common organisation of the markets in the sugar sector (3), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1148/98, and in particular Article 9(6) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 30. juuni 1981. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1785/81 suhkrusektori turgude &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (3) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1148/98, eriti selle artikli 9 l&otilde;iget 6, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 9(3) of Regulation (EEC) No 1785/81 states that it may be decided to grant production refunds on the products indicated in Article 1(1) (a) and (f) of that Regulation and the syrups indicated in Article 1(1) (d) that are in one of the situations indicated in Article 9(2) of the Treaty and are used in the manufacture of certain chemical industry products; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1785/81 artikli 9 l&otilde;ikes 3 s&auml;testatakse, et tootmistoetust v&otilde;idakse anda k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 1 l&otilde;ike 1 punktides a ja f osutatud toodete ja artikli 1 l&otilde;ike 1 punktis d osutatud siirupite jaoks, mis on m&otilde;nes asutamislepingu artikli 9 l&otilde;ikes 2 osutatud olukorras ja mida kasutatakse teatavate keemiat&ouml;&ouml;stustoodete valmistamiseks; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Regulation (EEC) No 1010/86 lays down general rules on determination of these production refunds and specifies the chemical products the manufacture of which permits a refund on the basic products; whereas Articles 5, 6 and 7 of that Regulation specify respectively how the production refund on each of the basic products raw sugar, sucrose syrups and unprocessed isoglucose is derived from the refund set on white sugar; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 1010/86 s&auml;testatakse k&otilde;nealuste tootmistoetuste kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramise &uuml;ldeeskirjad ja t&auml;psustatakse keemiatooted, mille valmistamiseks on lubatud anda p&otilde;hitoodete toetust; k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artiklites 5, 6 ja 7 t&auml;psustatakse, et p&otilde;hitoodete, s.o toorsuhkru, suhkrusiirupite ja t&ouml;&ouml;tlemata isogl&uuml;koosi tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;r on tuletatud valge suhkru toetusest; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 4a of Regulation (EEC) No 1010/86 states that the production refund per 100 kilograms of white sugar is to be fixed on the basis of the world market price for white sugar, increased by a standard amount of ECU 7 per 100 kilograms, and the price of Community sugar; whereas pursuant to Article 1(3) of Council Regulation (EC) No 150/95 of 23 January 1995 amending Regulation (EEC) No 3813/92 on the unit of account and the conversion rates to be applied for the purposes of the common agricultural policy (4) this standard amount was weighted by the coefficient 1,207509 and thus became ECU 8,45 per 100 kilograms of white sugar; whereas Article 4a(1a) of Regulation (EEC) No 1010/86 allows the Commission using the procedure specified in Article 41 of Regulation (EEC) No 1785/81, to reduce this amount as far as ECU 2,42; whereas experience with the production refund provisions since the new sugar sector production arrangements came into force in 1995 shows a need to facilitate as far as possible convergence of the circumstances of the Community chemical industry and those of chemical producers drawing supplies from the world sugar market; whereas the standard amount should therefore be reduced to ECU 6,45 for a two-year trial period; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1010/86 artiklis 4a s&auml;testatakse, et tootmistoetus 100 kg valge suhkru kohta m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks valge suhkru maailmaturuhinna p&otilde;hjal, mida on suurendatud 7 ek&uuml;&uuml; suuruse standardsumma v&otilde;rra 100 kg kohta, ning &uuml;henduse suhkru hinna p&otilde;hjal; vastavalt n&otilde;ukogu 23. jaanuari 1995. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 150/95 (millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 3813/92 &uuml;hises p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitikas kohaldatavate arvestus&uuml;hiku ja &uuml;mberarvestuskursside kohta (4)) artikli 1 l&otilde;ikele 3 on standardsummat korrutatud koefitsiendiga 1,207509 ja saadud tulemuseks 8,45 ek&uuml;&uuml;d 100 kg valge suhkru kohta; m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1010/86 artikli 4a l&otilde;ige 1a v&otilde;imaldab komisjonil kasutada k&otilde;nealuse summa v&auml;hendamiseks 2,42 ek&uuml;&uuml;ni m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1785/81 artiklis 41 t&auml;psustatud menetlust; kogemus tootmistoetuse s&uuml;steemi toimimise kohta alates uue tootmiskorra j&otilde;ustumisest suhkrusektoris 1995. aastal osutab vajadusele aidata v&otilde;imalikult palju kaasa &uuml;henduse keemiat&ouml;&ouml;stuse tingimuste l&auml;hendamisele maailmaturult tarnitud suhkrut kasutavate keemiat&ouml;&ouml;stuste tingimustele; seep&auml;rast tuleks standardsummat kaheaastaseks katseperioodiks v&auml;hendada 6,45 ek&uuml;&uuml;ni; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Commission Regulation (EEC) No 1729/78 of 24 July 1978 laying down detailed rules of application in respect of the production refund for sugar used in the chemical industry (5), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1730/97 (6), lays down provisions on determination of the production refund; whereas Article 1 thereof stipulates that it is to be set quarterly from 1 July, 1 October, 1 January and 1 April; whereas the production refund should therefore be set for a period as indicated in the said Article 1; </inglise>
<eesti> komisjoni 24. juuli 1978. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1729/78, milles s&auml;testatakse keemiat&ouml;&ouml;stuses kasutatava suhkru tootmistoetuse &uuml;ksikasjalikud rakenduseeskirjad, (5) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1730/97, (6) n&auml;hakse ette tootmistoetuse kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramise s&auml;tted; k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artiklis 1 s&auml;testatakse, et seda tuleb teha kord kvartalis 1. juulil, 1. oktoobril, 1. jaanuaril ja 1. aprillil algavateks ajavahemikeks; tootmistoetus tuleks seep&auml;rast kehtestada k&otilde;nealuses artiklis 1 osutatud ajavahemikeks; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, as a result of modification of the definitions of white sugar and raw sugar given in Article 1(2) (a) and (b) of Regulation (EEC) No 1785/81, sugars that have been flavoured or had colorants or other substances added no longer fall under these definitions and are therefore to be considered as 'other sugars'; whereas, however, under Article 1 of Regulation (EEC) No 1010/86 they count as basic products for the purposes of the production refund; whereas for determination of the production refund on these products a calculation method should therefore be set using their sucrose content; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1785/81 artikli 1 l&otilde;ike 2 punktides a ja b esitatud valge suhkru ja toorsuhkru m&auml;&auml;ratluste muutmise tulemusel ei kuulu maitse-, v&auml;rvaine- v&otilde;i muude lisanditega suhkrud enam k&otilde;nealuste m&auml;&auml;ratluste alla ja neid k&auml;sitatakse "muude suhkrutena"; m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1010/86 artikli 1 alusel k&auml;sitatakse neid p&otilde;hitoodetena, millele v&otilde;ib anda tootmistoetust; k&otilde;nealuste toodete tootmistoetuse kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramiseks tuleks s&auml;testada nende sahharoosisisaldusel p&otilde;hinev arvutusmeetod; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Sugar, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las suhkruturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The following paragraph is added to Article 4a of Regulation (EEC) No 1010/86: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1010/86 artiklile 4a lisatakse j&auml;rgmine l&otilde;ige: </eesti>
<inglise> '1b. </inglise>
<eesti> "1b. </eesti>
<inglise> For the period 1 October 1998 to 30 September 2000 the standard amount referred to in paragraph 1 shall be reduced to ECU 6,45. </inglise>
<eesti> Ajavahemikuks 1. oktoobrist 1998 kuni 30. septembrini 2000 v&auml;hendatakse l&otilde;ikes 1 osutatud standardsummat 6,45 ek&uuml;&uuml;ni." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The production refund for white sugar referred to in Article 4 of Regulation (EEC) No 1010/86 shall be ECU 41,963 per 100 kilograms net for the period 1 October to 31 December 1998. </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1010/86 artiklis 4 osutatud valge suhkru tootmistoetus ajavahemikus 1. oktoobrist 31. detsembrini 1998 on 41,963 ek&uuml;&uuml;d 100 netokilogrammi kohta. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on 1 October 1998. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub 1. oktoobril 1998. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 29 September 1998. </inglise>
